description:
This is a 30 minute workout called 'Intense VO2 Cycling Efforts! | 30 Minute Indoor Cycling Workout' from the channel GCN Training.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Challenging and Extreme.

Original workout description: This session focuses on bursts of high-power efforts to push your VO2 threshold. This workout will help to increase your body's oxygen efficiency and overall cardio fitness! Work hard and earn those rests in between these hard, 5-minute cycling efforts.
